	<h1 class="title">法国有份报纸，为恐怖袭击中逝去的每个人写了讣告</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">陈馨怡 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-07 19:45:15 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/18632/medium/18632.jpg?1449469602" alt="" />			
	</div>
